{"tid":121504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七警罪成】不滿7警被定罪 高達斌高院庭外示威","createTime":"2017-02-15T09:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T01:02:29.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"847da3a652cf9070842434b172bc82238ed33a1a","tid":121504,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170215/large/1487150786_fd02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170215%2Flarge%2F1487150786_fd02.jpg&h=96c32ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛港之聲主席高達斌因不滿「暗角7警」被裁定襲擊致他人受傷罪罪成，今聯同珍惜群組等成員到高等法院門外示威，手持聲稱由「一群非常憤怒的香港市民」聯署的「致律政司公開信」，內容提到「法官審判令裁決顛倒，究竟是乜鏡高懸」，又指「律政司只憑電視新聞片斷、聲稱遇襲疑犯供詞，斷案神速！」<br />\n<br />\n信的內容亦提及「要求律政司給予香港市民一合理解釋、要求律政司盡快把佔中暴徒一視同仁定罪、盡快向黑金主謀、佔中策劃煽動者四十多人提出檢控」等。"},{"pid":"8f13e327ac17a1019c253c47d992c9d60ac09fa1","tid":121504,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"班沉默大多數出哂黎未？"},{"pid":"67e331d360691e8ad1d369e7032f9dd27d801f0c","tid":121504,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:27:56.000Z","msg":"班仆街咪上次襲擊羅三七果班，睇下見唔見D暴徒先！"},{"pid":"ef4adf65c500c7a136f652d35967afe463fc0d12","tid":121504,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"呢班牛鬼蛇神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9428f2b3a4ca1448bf9878f302410ffba9443c9c","tid":121504,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"拖左咁耐都斷案神速？"},{"pid":"941659639463c51bb6a8db6b7d1b553699327c50","tid":121504,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拖左咁耐都斷案神速？</blockquote><br />\n佢地唔知自己講緊咩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc74e2d6115ea3ec625e4d4614287f12f428a7a","t